videos.description: Jaylen Brown drives and throws up an alley-oop to Daniel Theis who dunks on the opposite side of the basket.

videos.headline: Brown lobs to Theis for the slam

videos.description: In what was a gritty defensive game, the Celtics are able to power through the hard-nosed Pacers for a 116-111 win led by Jayson Tatum's 27 points and 11 rebounds.
